Create "User Variables" in Environment Variables like this.

Variable Name: ANDROID_PLATFORM_TOOLS
Variable Location for Nvidia Codeworks: "C:\NVPACK\android-sdk-windows\platform-tools"
Variable Location for Visual Studio: "C:\Program Files (x86)\Android\android-sdk\platform-tools"

Variable Name: ANDROID_TOOLS
Variable Location for Nvidia Codeworks: "C:\NVPACK\android-sdk-windows\tools"
Variable Location for Visual Studio: "C:\Program Files (x86)\Android\android-sdk\tools"

Insert these locations to the path:
%ANDROID_PLATFORM_TOOLS%
%ANDROID_TOOLS%

Restart Computer

Other Locations for Visual Studio Android Development Tools
Android SDK: C:/Program Files (x86)/Android/android-sdk
Android NDK: C:/ProgramData/Microsoft/AndroidNDK64/android-ndk-r13b
Apache ANT: C:/Program Files (x86)/Microsoft Visual Studio/2017/Enterprise/Apps/apache-ant-1.9.3
JDK: C:/Program Files/Java/jdk1.8.0_112
